				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I published a <a href="https://medium.com/@kwerb/bitcoin-is-gamification-e85c6a6eea22">post</a> over on Medium linking gamification and, of all thing, Bitcoin.  I&#8217;ve been spending some time lately thinking about Bitcoin and is underlying block chain mechanisms, which are fascinating.  I was surprised when I saw a connection to the work I&#8217;ve done in gamification.</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve also been meaning for a while to try out Medium, a popular new online publishing platform from Evan Williams, the guy behind Blogger and Twitter. So far, I like the experience. I&#8217;ll see whether I wind up moving more of my personal blogging there, instead of this site.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
